            "tab_title": "Mental Sharpness",
            "heading": "Clearer Airways, Clearer [[ Thinking ]]",
            "heading_tag": "h3",
            "description": "How you breathe shapes how you think. A recent fMRI study found that nasal breathing strengthens the connections across the brain networks you rely on for focus, attention, and higher-level thinking — the same systems behind clear, flexible thought and a calm, focused mind.",
            "quote": "",
            "custom_html": "<section class=\"member-spotlight\">\n  <div class=\"spotlight-card\">\n\n    <p class=\"spotlight-quote\">\n     “+40% higher-order brain connectivity during nasal breathing”\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .member-spotlight {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n\n  .spotlight-card {\n    background: #000000;\n    border-radius: 18px;\n    padding: 32px;\n    max-width: 520px;\n    width: 100%;\n    color: #FFFFFF;\n  }\n\n  .member-name {\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    margin: 0 0 28px;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  .spotlight-title {\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    margin: 0 0 36px;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  .spotlight-quote {\n    font-size: 26px;\n    line-height: 1.08;\n    margin: 0;\ncolor:#FFFFFF;\ntext-align:center;\n    letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n    font-family: 'pp-editorial', sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .spotlight-card {\n      padding: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .spotlight-quote {\n      font-size: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .spotlight-title {\n      font-size: 18px;\n    }\n\n    .member-name {\n      font-size: 18px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
