            "role_2": "Radiologist",
            "review_3": "Spatial Sleep has been a real game changer for me. I fall asleep so much faster and actually wake up feeling refreshed. I noticed a difference the very first night. Fell asleep faster, slept deeper. I used to toss and turn for hours, but with Spatial I'm out in minutes and I wake up rested.",
